## 📊 PROJECT STATUS

- **Core Architecture:** ✅ Complete (modular, clean separation)
- **Extension System:** ✅ Complete (30+ tools, providers, hooks)
- **Package Management:** ✅ Complete (CLI, resource resolution)
- **Logging:** ✅ Complete (JSON/Pretty, context logging)
- **Interactive Mode:** ⚠️ Basic (using package default, missing advanced features)
- **Session Management:** ❌ Missing (no resume/fork/continue)
- **Model Scoping:** ❌ Missing (no Ctrl+P cycling)
- **File Arguments:** ❌ Missing (no @file support)
- **Multi-mode:** ❌ Missing (no print/json/rpc)

